vernac_cmds: Lemma sigma_rooted_fun2 : forall (s s1 s2 : Site) (d : Message), s2 <> owner -> s1 <> s -> s2 <> s -> rooted_fun s s1 s2 d = 0%Z.
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun3 : forall s1 : Site, sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec LS (fun s : Site => rooted_fun s s1 owner dec) = 0%Z.
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun4 : forall (s s1 : Site) (l : list Site), ~ In s l -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec l (fun s0 : Site => rooted_fun s0 s1 owner (inc_dec s)) = 0%Z.
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun6 : forall (s s1 : Site) (l : list Site), ~ In s l -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec l (fun s0 : Site => rooted_fun s0 s owner copy) = 0%Z.
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun7 : forall (s : Site) (l : list Site), only_once Site eq_site_dec s l -> s <> owner -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec l (fun s0 : Site => rooted_fun s0 s owner copy) = 1%Z.
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun8 : forall (s2 : Site) (l : list Site), ~ In s2 l -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec l (fun s : Site => rooted_fun s owner s2 dec) = 0%Z.
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun9 : forall (s2 : Site) (l : list Site), only_once Site eq_site_dec s2 l -> s2 <> owner -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec l (fun s : Site => rooted_fun s owner s2 dec) = 1%Z.
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun10 : forall s2 : Site, sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec LS (fun s : Site => rooted_fun s owner s2 copy) = 0%Z.
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun11 : forall (s1 s2 : Site) (l : list Site), s2 <> owner -> s1 <> owner -> ~ In s2 l -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec l (fun s : Site => rooted_fun s s1 s2 dec) = 0%Z.
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun12 : forall s1 s2 : Site, s2 <> owner -> s1 <> owner -> only_once Site eq_site_dec s2 LS -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec LS (fun s : Site => rooted_fun s s1 s2 dec) = 1%Z.
generalize (sigma_rooted_fun11 s1 s2 l H H0).
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun13 : forall (s1 s2 : Site) (l : list Site), s2 <> owner -> s1 <> owner -> ~ In s1 l -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec l (fun s : Site => rooted_fun s s1 s2 copy) = 0%Z.

Lemma sigma_rooted_fun14 : forall (s1 s2 : Site) (l : list Site), s2 <> owner -> s1 <> owner -> only_once Site eq_site_dec s1 l -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec l (fun s : Site => rooted_fun s s1 s2 copy) = 1%Z.
generalize (sigma_rooted_fun13 s1 s2 l0 H H0).
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun5 : forall s s1 : Site, only_once Site eq_site_dec s LS -> s <> owner -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec LS (fun s0 : Site => rooted_fun s0 s1 owner (inc_dec s)) = 1%Z.
Lemma sigma_rooted_fun1 : forall (s s1 s2 : Site) (d : Message), s2 <> owner -> ~ In s1 LS -> ~ In s2 LS -> sigma_but Site owner eq_site_dec LS (fun s : Site => rooted_fun s s1 s2 d) = 0%Z.
intros s s1 s2 d H.
generalize H2; simpl in |- *; intro; intro.
Lemma add_reduce4 : forall x y z a : Z, (x + y)%Z = (z + a)%Z -> (x - a)%Z = (z - y)%Z.
Lemma add_reduce5 : forall x y z a : Z, (x - a)%Z = (z - y)%Z -> x = (a + z - y)%Z.
Lemma add_reduce6 : forall x y z : Z, x = (z + y)%Z -> (x - z)%Z = y.

command: generalize (sigma_rooted_fun11 s1 s2 l H H0).
generalize (sigma_rooted_fun13 s1 s2 l0 H H0).
intros s s1 s2 d H.
generalize H2; simpl in |- *; intro; intro.
